# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok about one-fifth of the ###,### palestinian government employees will receive a small down payment on long-overdue salaries , officials said friday .
# ::alignments
(s / say-01
      :ARG0 (p / person
            :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                  :ARG2 (o / official)))
      :ARG1 (r / receive-01
            :ARG0 (p2 / person
                  :ARG1-of (ii / include-91
                        :ARG2 (p3 / person
                              :ARG1-of (e / employ-01
                                    :ARG0 (g / government-organization
                                          :ARG0-of (g2 / govern-01
                                                :ARG1 (c / country
                                                      :name (n / name
                                                            :op1 "Palestine"))))))
                        :ARG3 (a / about
                              :op1 "1/5"))
                  :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                        :ARG1 c
                        :ARG2 (m / member)))
            :ARG1 (p4 / pay-01
                  :ARG1 (s2 / salary
                        :ARG1-of (d / due-01
                              :ARG1-of (l / long-03)))
                  :mod (s3 / small)
                  :mod (d2 / down)))
      :time (d3 / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday)))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok despite of still refusing to consider vietnam a full market economy , the european union -lrb- eu -rrb- has just granted vietnam the `` ad hoc market economy regime '' , which benefits the country in case of trade disputes .
# ::alignments
(h / have-concession-91
      :ARG1 (g / grant-01
            :ARG0 (o / organization
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "European"
                        :op2 "Union"))
            :ARG1 (r / regime
                  :mod (e / economy
                        :mod (m / market))
                  :mod (a / ad-hoc)
                  :ARG0-of (b / benefit-01
                        :ARG1 (c / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Vietnam"))
                        :condition (d / dispute-01
                              :ARG2 (t / trade-01))))
            :ARG2 c
            :mod (j / just))
      :ARG2 (r2 / refuse-01
            :ARG0 o
            :ARG1 (c2 / consider-01
                  :ARG0 o
                  :ARG1 (e2 / economy
                        :mod (f / full)
                        :mod (m2 / market)
                        :domain c))
            :mod (s / still)))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred

                  :op2 "Ag"))

                  :quant 2
                  :mod (e / engine)

                  :location (f2 / facility
                        :mod (m / main)
                        :poss c
                        :location (c2 / city
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Stuttgart"))))
            :ARG2 (m2 / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000000
                  :unit (d / dollar))))

                                          :quant 1
                                          :unit (y / year))))))
            :ord (o / ordinal-entity
                  :value 100))
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (f / friday)))

(b / bring-01
      :ARG0 (m / marry-01
            :ARG1 (m2 / media)
            :ARG2 (c / company
                  :name (n / name
                        :op1 "Cbs"))
            :ARG1-of (h / have-degree-91
                  :ARG2 (b2 / big)
                  :ARG3 (m3 / most)
                  :ARG5 (h2 / history)))
      :ARG1 (a / and
            :op1 (c2 / company
                  :name (n2 / name
                        :op1 "Viacom"
                        :op2 "Inc."))
            :op2 c)
      :ARG2 c
      :ARG3 (m4 / merge-01
            :ARG1 c2
            :ARG2 c
            :ARG3 (m5 / monetary-quantity
                  :quant 1000000000
                  :unit (d / dollar))
            :ARG0-of (c3 / create-01
                  :ARG1 (c4 / conglomerate
                        :ARG1-of (n3 / new-01)
                        :mod (g / globe)
                        :ARG1-of (p / present-02
                              :ARG2 (a2 / and
                                    :op1 (t / television)
                                    :op2 (m6 / movie)
                                    :op3 (r / radio)
                                    :op4 (b3 / book)
                                    :op5 (b4 / billboard))
                              :mod (v / vast)))))
      :ARG4 c
      :time (d2 / date-entity
            :weekday (t2 / tuesday)))
